$interpreted: NEKO#ΦωΦ: Hey, Roger or what's-your-name, how selfish can you be!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Just like how much you value Kittyeyes, Kittyeyes will never~ ever~abandon the person most important to her and run away all by herself!
PAFF: NEKO...
Bandit Goon: DIE!!!
PAFF: NEKO, look out!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: PAFF, you...
PAFF: NEKO, focus on your target...I have your back...!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ......!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...You, how could you...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: How could you be cooler than NEKO~!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You pathetic weaklings with your power levels of 5~You shall never stop us from clearing this level!!
Bandit Goon: Now you're asking for it!!!
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger! Are you alright!
Roger: Of course I'm alright! What about you? Are you injured!?
PAFF: I think that those two...must've experienced a lot of things together.
PAFF: They rely on each other, which is why they both treasure each other. Nothing can replace their bond.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: NEKO thought that it was Kittyeyes who was reliant on Roger.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Looks like he relies on Kittyeyes as well.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ah, right. Back there...th...thanks.
PAFF: NEKO...
PAFF: No, I'm the one who has to thank NEKO...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Thank me? For what?
PAFF: To be honest...I have a memory disorder. I don't remember things from the past.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Memory disorder!? So the rumors were true...
PAFF: For a long time, I've always felt like I'm a hollow puppet.
PAFF: It's just like what NEKO said...I'm just an overly advertised idol who knows nothing besides singing...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: I'm sorry...NEKO went too far when I said that...
PAFF: It's okay. Besides, I understand now.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Understand what?
PAFF: Even though NEKO...may not really like me...
PAFF: ...the fact that we came to this dangerous world together, it's best...that we rely on each other.
PAFF: ...Just like those two.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: PAFF...
PAFF: The only thing I can and know how to do is sing. Maybe that's all I can do...but here, my singing can help NEKO out.
PAFF: This is...a decision I made myself.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...Eh, so that's...you want to say thank you to NEKO...all because of that?
PAFF: Well...yeah.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: How...how can you be so stupid!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: T-this is no big deal. There's, n-no need for you to thank me for anything!
Nolva: Ah, found them!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nora-chan! Nolva-chan!
Nolva: Kittyeyes? Roger? What are you guys doing here...?
PAFF: So Miss Nolva knows Roger and Miss Kittyeyes?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: This video game world is surprisingly small!
PAFF: Ah, Nora, I came across this on the way...
Nora: ...It appears to still be functional. You have my gratitude.
Nolva: However, those injuries...what on earth happened?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: It's a story of how the hero NEKO took down the super nasty bandit leader!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: I feel like we can get a spinoff movie going with this! How about this, NEKO will compose the theme song and PAFF can sing it...
PAFF: Haha...
Kittyeyes: It really is a coincidence. Since everybody seems to know each other, how about you come to our home first!
Roger: Ah, my home right now is probably a little...
Kittyeyes: ...Messy? Come on, it has always been like that. What's the difference? So, can we, brother Roger?

Roger: A-Alright then. However, it's getting late.
Let's find a safe place to get some rest first.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nora-chan, we're leaving!
Nora: ...These messages are...
